snippet.title: Viewfinder - Demo and Release Date Announcement Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10006160

Challenge perception, redefine reality, and reshape the world around you with an instant camera. Viewfinder is a new single player game offering hours of interesting and fun experiences while uncovering the mysteries left behind.

Viewfinder is a mind-bending first person adventure game in which you can bring pictures to life by placing them into the world. Create, Destroy, and Rewind: Viewfinder is releasing on July 18, Play the Demo on PlayStation 5 Now

#ps5 #ps5games
